description:
This is a 35 minute workout called '30 MIN CARDIO PILATES || At-Home Full Body Workout' from the channel Move With Nicole.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Pilates and Cardio/HIIT.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Advanced fitness levels.
The workout has a The Endorphin Wave and The Groove Session vibe.
The technique difficulty is Intermediate.
The effort required is Moderate.

Original workout description: Break a sweat with this new 30 Minute Cardio Pilates Workout. This Full Body Workout will combine Pilates principles/movements with athletic cardio flows to increase your heart rate for a fun and sweaty session! Low impact and high impact options will be provided, so you pick the intensity! I hope you enjoy it and let me know how you go in the comments below. :)
